" I saw people going like Star Trek and they were laying hands on people and they were getting baptized in the Holy Ghost, and the glory of the Lord was showing up in those houses and they were being radically healed and delivered by the power of God.

01:01:07.892 --> 01:01:11.760
As you finished, He would take you back home.

01:01:11.760 --> 01:01:22.480
He said, "I'll let you even film it on your phone to validate that you were there as a sign and a wonder in these last days.

01:01:22.480 --> 01:01:25.620
I'll let you validate the area.

01:01:27.489 --> 01:01:28.229
" You know what I'm talking about?

01:01:28.229 --> 01:01:35.269
Like you not exposing the people in there so they lose their life; God's not stupid.

01:01:35.269 --> 01:01:38.499
But it was like a witness somehow.

01:01:43.463 --> 01:01:43.691
I don't know how, like you're there and you're traveling around.

01:01:43.691 --> 01:01:53.485
Maybe you won't go into someone's house in North Korea and film them and say, "I want to video you and have ministry.

01:01:53.485 --> 01:02:04.307
" I'm not trying to be flaky with this; this is how the Lord showed me, folks.

01:02:09.200 --> 01:02:09.440
You know what I'm saying?

01:02:09.440 --> 01:02:11.449
And it was translating all over the place.

01:02:20.533 --> 01:02:20.799
It was not just one place; it was all in South America.

01:02:20.799 --> 01:02:22.159
I saw it translating.

01:02:25.022 --> 01:02:26.107
I saw—am I using the word right?

01:02:26.107 --> 01:02:30.990
—translate, to go all over the place, and the glory of the Lord showed up.

01:02:30.990 --> 01:02:37.931
Healings, demonstrations, and manifestations like you wouldn't believe; I'm telling you, souls are coming to the kingdom of God.

01:02:37.931 --> 01:02:46.034
He said, "You're asking me to come, but there's millions of people in North Korea that have never heard the gospel.

01:02:50.719 --> 01:02:50.999
" A highway—it's what He called it—a supernatural highway.

01:02:52.499 --> 01:03:07.173
And I'm going to take you into Asia and you'll be preaching, and you'll be in a prayer group and all of a sudden you'll be in North Korea, you'll be in Vietnam, and I'll have you there.

01:03:26.530 --> 01:03:26.780
And He said you'll hear their language and you'll speak their language and know exactly what they're saying through supernatural interpretation.

01:03:36.057 --> 01:03:36.365
You're saying transport.

01:03:36.365 --> 01:03:38.839
Transport through language, no language barriers.

01:03:38.839 --> 01:03:47.730
You'll know North Korea, you'll know whatever, and you'll be able to just talk to them and they'll be able to talk to you.

01:03:47.730 --> 01:03:53.820
There will be a supernatural on your mind.

01:03:53.820 --> 01:03:56.400
I saw working with the angelic host.

01:04:02.302 --> 01:04:02.506
The Lord said, "You will work with the angels.

01:04:02.506 --> 01:04:07.806
You'll work with the angels in the days ahead as a sign.

01:04:18.719 --> 01:04:18.933
" He said, "I don't want any should perish, Brandon, but when this gospel is preached as a witness into all the earth, then will the end come.

01:04:18.933 --> 01:04:20.920
" North Korea cannot be left out.

01:04:20.920 --> 01:04:24.608
Iran's people can't be left out.

01:04:24.608 --> 01:04:29.937
He's coming; He's leaving the ninety-nine to go after the one.

01:04:29.937 --> 01:04:40.773
And He showed me even into the islands that have not been really witnessed to, He was going to show up.

01:04:40.773 --> 01:04:42.840
I saw the glory of the Lord.

01:04:42.840 --> 01:04:52.384
As I saw all this and I saw what He was about to do with the North Koreans and all this stuff, I got so excited after I got finished with this video.

01:05:05.180 --> 01:05:05.450
I haven't been able to stop thinking about it.

01:05:05.450 --> 01:05:08.666
I know what the Lord showed me.

01:05:08.666 --> 01:05:11.733
I know what He said: that it's about the souls.

01:05:24.280 --> 01:05:24.660
He died for them.

01:05:27.560 --> 01:05:31.862
And I'll continue to tell you about the holes in His hands and the holes in His feet.

01:05:31.862 --> 01:05:40.699
As He walked, He showed me the harvest, similar to what John Kilpatrick was standing by; the harvest was plentiful and the laborers are few.

01:05:53.829 --> 01:05:54.354
He said, "It's all hands on deck.

01:05:54.354 --> 01:05:58.916
This is an all-hands-on-deck moment.

01:06:04.976 --> 01:06:05.168
" I'm looking for the person who will just say, "Yes, here am I, Lord.

01:06:05.168 --> 01:06:05.743
Send me.

01:06:05.743 --> 01:06:07.351
" I'll go to Walmart today.

01:06:07.351 --> 01:06:12.699
I'll talk to the little widow lady who doesn't have anyone to talk to on the park bench.

01:06:12.699 --> 01:06:18.207
I'll go to the playground and talk to the single mothers.

01:06:20.120 --> 01:06:31.259
I wouldn't be saying guys out there to talk to them, but I'm saying to the mothers that would say, "Hey, I want to be a light to you.

01:06:31.259 --> 01:06:33.013
" Do you know what I'm saying?

01:06:33.013 --> 01:06:37.120
Just being a light everywhere you go.

01:06:37.120 --> 01:06:55.609
That's why I said make a list of how many people you believe God for this year, how many people you want to see get led to Jesus.

01:06:56.690 --> 01:07:03.940
I say, "Hey, if you only got one person saved this year, have a goal of at least five.

01:07:03.940 --> 01:07:18.068
" Stretch yourself in 2026 to believe God for bigger financially, spiritually, for your marriage, for your kids to get saved, for your cousins, I don't know.

01:07:18.068 --> 01:07:30.079
But I want you to believe God for big in 2026 as He's cleaning His church up, as He's getting the bride ready, as He's getting things ready.

01:07:30.079 --> 01:07:38.000
I'm telling you, we're about to see things like you wouldn't believe, y'all.

01:07:45.549 --> 01:07:45.979
But He wants you to have a prayer group.

01:07:45.979 --> 01:07:53.543
We're going to keep growing this channel, believing all to the glory of God.

01:07:53.543 --> 01:07:56.160
We'll hit over a million.

01:08:03.199 --> 01:08:03.653
I don't know; we'll see on this side or the other.

01:08:03.653 --> 01:08:06.759
I'm talking about South Korea.

01:08:22.543 --> 01:08:22.847
I know what He said, but I'm saying if it happens all in 2026, praise God.

01:08:37.199 --> 01:08:37.483
I believed it was going to happen this year, and right now I'm still not hitting 600,000, so I'm believing God it will do it next year.

01:08:43.417 --> 01:08:43.748
But if it doesn't, you just keep hitting it.

01:08:43.748 --> 01:08:49.200
It's the little drop in the cave that makes the indention.

01:08:49.200 --> 01:08:52.377
It's the little drop over a course of time.

01:08:52.377 --> 01:08:57.626
Don't get disappointed when the little drop doesn't show up and make an indention.

01:08:59.910 --> 01:09:00.132
It takes time.

01:09:16.560 --> 01:09:17.248
One drop at a time makes the mark.

01:09:19.312 --> 01:09:27.471
You walk in a cave and say, "How did that happen overnight?

01:09:27.471 --> 01:09:30.051
" No, that happened over time—quite some time.

01:09:30.051 --> 01:09:34.993
Some people say that's over thousands of years.

01:09:34.993 --> 01:09:42.160
And I'm like, "Wow, isn't that amazing?

01:09:42.160 --> 01:09:46.149
" Those stalactites and stalagmites that happened over thousands of years; it's inconsistency.

01:09:46.149 --> 01:09:49.176
It's being consistent with whatever God's called you to do.

01:09:49.176 --> 01:09:51.680
Don't get weary in well-doing, church.

01:09:51.680 --> 01:09:54.064
Keep your head up high.

01:09:54.064 --> 01:10:03.920
Yeah, we see the storms and all the stuff going on around us, but we need to be the salt.

01:10:18.338 --> 01:10:18.569
And don't lose your saltiness in all the pressure that you're going through.

01:10:18.569 --> 01:10:39.755
Whether your finances feel hardship right now in your household with all the things they said—the economy is great, inflation's down—I don't know where they're at.

01:10:50.020 --> 01:10:50.320
They live on Capitol Hill.

01:10:50.320 --> 01:10:58.568
They've got big paychecks up there and they're getting paid by our tax dollars.

01:10:58.568 --> 01:11:02.331
They live like kings.

01:11:02.834 --> 01:11:20.280
You go, "Well, I don't know where you're at, sir, but I want you to come to Oklahoma and say the inflation's better, the housing market's better.

01:11:20.280 --> 01:11:22.708
" Okay, we'll see.

01:11:22.708 --> 01:11:30.620
You go, "I don't know what you're on, but you're not in reality over here.

01:11:30.620 --> 01:11:44.000
" As much as I want to be excited about what you're saying, we live in the real world.

01:11:49.740 --> 01:11:50.040
You live on the hill.

01:11:50.040 --> 01:11:59.440
It's interesting to me, you know, where some people want to try to hype things up, but we'll just keep fighting.

01:11:59.440 --> 01:12:01.720
We fight the good fight of faith.

01:12:01.720 --> 01:12:04.560
Now, we're going to pray for New Year's Eve.

01:12:04.560 --> 01:12:07.700
We're going to pray for President Trump's protection.

01:12:07.700 --> 01:12:11.074
We will continue to stand and protect Kai.

01:12:11.074 --> 01:12:13.519
We pray for his granddaughter.

01:12:13.519 --> 01:12:16.493
We pray for John Jr.

01:12:16.493 --> 01:12:23.440
, Eric, praying for them to come up with this creative idea for crypto and all the things the Lord's shown us about that.

01:12:23.440 --> 01:12:27.307
I still believe with all my heart the Lord showed me certain cryptos.

01:12:27.307 --> 01:12:30.500
Yeah, it took a nosedive this week, didn't it?

01:12:30.500 --> 01:12:32.789
I was like, "Oh no, it's going to zero.

01:12:32.789 --> 01:12:34.720
Oh no, it's going to zero.

01:12:34.720 --> 01:12:36.960
" That's what it felt like.

01:12:36.960 --> 01:12:37.919
Oh no.

01:12:37.919 --> 01:12:43.320
But Braden goes, "Dad, I don't want to look at it.

01:12:45.169 --> 01:12:46.069
" I said, "Neither do I.

01:12:46.069 --> 01:12:47.870
Neither do I.

01:12:59.307 --> 01:12:59.564
" You know, but we know what the Lord has shown us in the future.

01:13:02.274 --> 01:13:05.900
I believe with all my heart that something's going to come out of this.

01:13:24.940 --> 01:13:29.200
You know, are we missing it?

01:13:29.200 --> 01:13:30.240
I pray not.

01:13:30.240 --> 01:13:32.730
I pray, you know what?

01:13:47.780 --> 01:13:48.110
We hear in part, we see in part.

01:13:59.259 --> 01:13:59.559
I'm not telling you I have everything right, folks.

01:14:01.333 --> 01:14:05.200
I'm doing the best I can, just like you do with your walk with the Word.

01:14:05.947 --> 01:14:20.503
But it's easy to stand from the peanut gallery and be a critic when you're not doing anything for God at all.

01:14:20.503 --> 01:14:31.244
And the loudest people in the section are usually the ones doing nothing for Him at all.

01:14:31.244 --> 01:14:47.440
And they yell at the people who are trying their hardest, and they have the big 'L' sign on the side: "You're a loser.

01:14:47.440 --> 01:14:48.933
You've got nothing going for you.

01:15:04.480 --> 01:15:04.810
" And you look at them and go, "But what did you do this year?

01:15:04.810 --> 01:15:10.893
How many people did you lead to Christ this year?

01:15:10.893 --> 01:15:15.004
How many people did you pray for?

01:15:15.253 --> 01:15:21.360
" And all the criticism from the peanut gallery—shut up.

01:15:21.360 --> 01:15:24.240
You know, we're all trying.

01:15:35.280 --> 01:15:35.810
The ones that are trying, keep trying.

01:15:44.010 --> 01:15:46.470
I knew whenever the Lord was talking to me about the stripes—"By His stripes, you are healed.

01:15:46.470 --> 01:15:49.668
" Fall down on the concrete and skin your knee.

01:15:52.920 --> 01:15:53.220
And how bad does that hurt?

01:15:53.220 --> 01:16:01.040
It's excruciating for somebody, especially if you're elderly, and you just take all the skin off.

01:16:01.040 --> 01:16:19.168
Imagine having a cat o' nine tails whipping your back and tearing that flesh off.

01:16:25.954 --> 01:16:26.286
He went through it all for you to live in victory.

01:16:34.640 --> 01:16:35.398
That wasn't a skinned knee, as bad as that hurts.

01:16:47.520 --> 01:16:48.091
You can picture that, can't you?

01:16:48.091 --> 01:16:53.577
What if you pinch yourself and it's really real?

01:16:53.577 --> 01:17:07.510
It hurts a little bit whenever you maybe stuck your hand in the car door or something and it hurts really bad.

01:17:10.960 --> 01:17:12.410
Jesus went through hell for every single one of us.

01:17:12.410 --> 01:17:14.930
More than just a skinned knee.

01:17:14.930 --> 01:17:20.400
More than just a hand in the car door.

01:17:20.400 --> 01:17:33.760
I remember one time my dad was working as a carpenter using a nail gun and he was putting the nail in the air gun and it went through his hand.

01:17:33.760 --> 01:17:44.150
His buddy Tommy had to take a crowbar and pull my dad's hand off of that board, if I remember correctly.

01:17:44.150 --> 01:17:53.900
He had to hold it because he couldn't get the blood on the wood because they were finishing it.

01:17:53.900 --> 01:18:01.520
So, his hand had to be pried off of the wood and the blood was trying to squirt all over the place.

01:18:01.520 --> 01:18:14.693
They grabbed it and had to wrap it in a cloth because they didn't want to stain the oak wood because they were working on really expensive houses.

01:18:21.582 --> 01:18:21.831
And it was excruciating.

01:18:21.831 --> 01:18:24.880
But Jesus took nails, big humongous nails.

01:18:29.784 --> 01:18:29.968
I saw the holes in His hand.

01:18:31.072 --> 01:18:44.510
This isn't something that's just some kind of fairy tale that we read to our kids before we go to sleep, like Goldilocks and the Three Bears or Little Red Riding Hood.

01:18:44.510 --> 01:18:53.840
Jesus Christ died for you, and it's not some fairy tale.

01:18:53.840 --> 01:19:01.136
He went through it just like when you skin your knee and you go through pain and it's excruciating.

01:19:01.136 --> 01:19:11.450
Jesus Christ took it all on His back and they ripped His flesh off His body and they put nails in His hands.

01:19:11.450 --> 01:19:16.640
They put a crown of thorns on His head.

01:19:16.640 --> 01:19:18.519
They ripped His beard out.

01:19:18.519 --> 01:19:20.480
They spat in His face.

01:19:20.480 --> 01:19:27.120
They hung Him on a cross and they shoved a spear in His side and blood and water flowed.

01:19:40.128 --> 01:19:40.280
A massive gash was in His side.

01:19:40.280 --> 01:19:43.213
He suffered greatly for you to walk in victory.

01:19:43.213 --> 01:20:05.554
I'll never forget one night I was sitting on the side of a bed—I know I'm going a little long but you need to hear it—I was talking to a man that was really overcoming arthritis and he said, "Brandon, how come all Christians aren't healed?

01:20:05.554 --> 01:20:07.653
Why aren't all Christians healed, Brandon?

01:20:09.920 --> 01:20:10.250
I don't understand.

01:20:10.250 --> 01:20:13.280
I've been suffering with this arthritis so bad.

01:20:13.280 --> 01:20:15.040
" His name was Stanley.

01:20:15.040 --> 01:20:23.618
His hand was always hurting with arthritis, and he couldn't understand why all Christians aren't healed.

01:20:24.560 --> 01:20:25.640
I said, "I don't know.

01:20:29.899 --> 01:20:30.249
I don't have the answer to it.

01:20:32.355 --> 01:20:36.666
" I laid down, went to bed, and I was taken out of my body.

01:20:36.666 --> 01:20:38.680
Jesus took me to the cross.

01:20:38.680 --> 01:20:41.973
He took me to the whipping post.

01:20:46.764 --> 01:20:48.080
I can tell you the temperature that it was outside: it was about 80 degrees.

01:20:48.080 --> 01:20:55.805
It had a stench in the atmosphere.

01:21:02.200 --> 01:21:02.420
I could smell some kind of animal livestock dung where He was at.

01:21:02.640 --> 01:21:08.560
I don't know how, but I could smell it.

01:21:18.533 --> 01:21:21.480
Jesus was standing right here—now, He was sitting right here—but I was watching Jesus in the past as a young man of 33 years old.

01:21:21.480 --> 01:21:24.880
His hands were tied to this whipping post.

01:21:38.080 --> 01:21:38.608
He was straddled up on this.

01:21:38.608 --> 01:21:43.540
And I saw Him up like this.

01:21:43.540 --> 01:21:51.303
And I saw one Roman soldier on one side and another one on this side.

01:21:51.303 --> 01:21:55.553
I watched both of those men.

01:22:05.600 --> 01:22:05.920
One man was probably 300 pounds.

01:22:05.920 --> 01:22:07.200
He was ginormous.

01:22:07.200 --> 01:22:14.864
He had a totally black outfit on, which I don't understand—that's what it looked like, some kind of weird garment.

01:22:14.864 --> 01:22:23.080
But the other was a Roman soldier that had Roman garb on like you would see in the movies.

01:22:29.253 --> 01:22:32.159
And I saw them take the cat o' nine tails and one whipped this side and the other one whipped this side.

01:22:32.159 --> 01:22:38.860
And as I saw that happen, I saw the flesh ripping off of His body and it was excruciating.

01:22:38.860 --> 01:22:41.591
It was dripping from His body—the bone, everything.

01:22:41.591 --> 01:22:46.080
It was the most grotesque thing I've ever seen.

01:22:46.480 --> 01:22:53.387
I saw the crown of thorns upon His head pressed down and blood was running down His forehead.

01:22:53.387 --> 01:23:01.520
His beard was missing pieces where they had ripped the beard out of His face.

01:23:01.520 --> 01:23:17.291
I remember I was standing over here as I was watching this happen and I was weeping and I was screaming but nobody could hear me and I said, "Stop!

01:23:20.920 --> 01:23:21.210
You must stop!

01:23:21.790 --> 01:23:25.417
" and I was screaming because they were beating Him with those whips.

01:23:25.417 --> 01:23:38.000
They were whipping His body and His body would tremble as they were whipping His body and the blood was so much on the ground it was like He was in a pool of blood.

01:23:38.000 --> 01:23:44.293
As they did it, I saw Jesus look up and I saw Him, out of His mouth, tell that one soldier, "I love you.

01:23:52.099 --> 01:23:52.369
I love you.

01:23:52.369 --> 01:23:53.509
" I saw it.

01:23:53.509 --> 01:24:02.959
His face looked up at him and it was the most sincere look in His eyes as they were laughing and they were beating His body.

01:24:05.1000 --> 01:24:07.199
Jesus was standing beside me over here as I watched this all happen.

01:24:07.199 --> 01:24:12.693
I can even tell you what His back looked like before they beat Him.

01:24:22.880 --> 01:24:23.360
He was not skinny looking; He was muscular looking.

01:24:23.360 --> 01:24:26.103
His skin looked olive.

01:24:36.240 --> 01:24:36.420
It looked glossy from oily sweat.

01:24:36.420 --> 01:24:48.239
You know how whenever you sweat and you get that oil on your body from not having a bath in a little bit?

01:24:54.773 --> 01:24:55.320
That's the way His back looked before they began.

01:24:55.320 --> 01:24:57.253
I watched it.

01:25:09.707 --> 01:25:10.040
The Lord spoke to me that day and He said to me, "What do you not understand about 'by My stripes you are healed,' Brandon?

01:25:10.040 --> 01:25:13.000
What do you not understand about this?

01:25:13.000 --> 01:25:21.600
" He said, "If somebody was to tell you that you weren't saved, that you weren't born again, you would fight them, wouldn't you?

01:25:24.586 --> 01:25:24.933
You would tell them, 'I am saved.

01:25:24.933 --> 01:25:31.919
' If they say, 'I don't believe you're saved,' you'd say, 'I am saved.

01:25:31.919 --> 01:25:33.404
I am delivered.

01:25:55.360 --> 01:25:55.679
I know He saved my soul by what He did for me.

01:25:55.679 --> 01:26:02.650
'" But the moment you feel sickness and disease, you doubt that you're healed.

01:26:02.650 --> 01:26:09.143
He said, "The same faith that it takes to get healed is the same faith that it takes to be saved.

01:26:09.143 --> 01:26:09.938
They're the same.

01:26:09.938 --> 01:26:15.440
" He said, "You don't realize what it takes for you to say, 'I was once lost, but now I'm found.

01:26:15.440 --> 01:26:18.160
I'm no longer going to hell.

01:26:18.160 --> 01:26:22.526
' You don't look at the miracle that truly is.

01:26:22.526 --> 01:26:28.206
But the same faith that you would fight somebody by telling them, 'I know I'm saved.

01:26:28.206 --> 01:26:36.099
'" They say, "No, I don't believe it.

01:26:39.540 --> 01:26:41.024
You still act the way you used to sometimes.

01:26:47.223 --> 01:26:47.509
I don't believe it.

01:26:51.560 --> 01:26:51.740
Are you really saved?

01:26:51.740 --> 01:26:53.497
" "No, I know I'm saved.

01:26:53.497 --> 01:26:55.259
I'm going to heaven.

01:26:55.259 --> 01:26:59.199
I'm not going to hell.

01:26:59.199 --> 01:27:05.440
" He said it takes the same faith to sit there and say, "I'm healed by Your stripes, Lord.

01:27:05.440 --> 01:27:19.306
" He said, "When you believe that the same way, Brandon, the manifestation comes as long as you hold on to it just like that.

01:27:19.306 --> 01:27:23.210
No matter if they talk you out of it.

01:27:23.210 --> 01:27:33.360
'I have a symptom, Lord.

01:27:33.360 --> 01:27:37.787
I have a symptom.

01:27:37.787 --> 01:27:46.135
My flesh is crying out.

01:27:46.135 --> 01:27:58.719
I've got this pain in my body.

01:27:58.719 --> 01:28:06.240
I've got this going on.

01:28:06.240 --> 01:29:20.520
' But it's the same way the pain of the soul is whenever you are messing up with sin and you have that, but you don't question your mind because of the symptom of it.

01:29:20.520 --> 01:29:34.263
I'm saved.

01:29:34.263 --> 01:30:00.411
I believe.

01:30:00.411 --> 01:30:03.760
I'm once saved, always saved.

01:30:03.760 --> 01:30:05.966
Don't you know that?

01:30:05.966 --> 01:30:09.270
Well, I'm once healed, always healed.

01:30:09.270 --> 01:30:12.251
I'm healed and whole and well.

01:30:12.251 --> 01:30:14.906
